description	"Juhani [Jedi Guardian]

^2Weaponry:
- Juhani's Lightsaber
-- Strong Style Only
-- Saber Defense (3)
-- Blaster Defense   (2)
-- Blaster Deflect (2)
-- Saber Throw (1) ^3[CS1]

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (2)
- Speed (3)
- Protect (3) ^3[CS3]
- Grip (3)

^8Attributes:
- Force Block (2)

Juhani, a Cathar Jedi Guardian during the Jedi Civil War, grew up on Taris after her family fled the Mandalorian assault on Cathar. Orphaned and sold into slavery to pay off debts, she was freed by Jedi Knight Revan, who encouraged her to become a Jedi. She then trained at the Jedi Enclave on Dantooine under Jedi Master Quatra."